description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Plezier purrs with a rating of 65, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 195, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Stringalong for East, 5 for South, and 3 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70653-57534-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [195 Votes, Top 5% Score]
